# ============================================================
# INCLUDE (tracked by Git):
# ============================================================
# Assets/Scripts/          - All C# scripts
# Assets/Shaders/          - Custom shaders
# Assets/ShaderGraphs/     - Shader graphs
# Assets/ComputeShaders/   - GPU compute shaders
# Assets/Materials/         - Custom materials
# Assets/Scenes/           - Scene files
# Assets/Prefabs/          - Custom prefabs
# Assets/Prefabs_ROSNET/   - ROS network prefabs
# Assets/Resources/        - Runtime-loaded assets
# Assets/RosMessages/      - ROS message definitions
# Assets/Editor/           - Editor scripts
# Assets/ai_interfaces/    - AI interface definitions
# Assets/Drone/            - Drone prefabs/config
# Assets/unity_robotics_demo_msgs/
# Packages/manifest.json   - Package dependencies
# ProjectSettings/         - Project configuration
